introduction.bio: My name is Gabriel, I am 20 years old, and I work as a Business Intelligence Analyst at JBS, where I focus on data analysis and generating strategic insights, using QlikSense to develop results-oriented solutions.
introduction.bio2: I am studying Information Systems at FIAP, enhancing my skills in technology, data management, and innovation, aiming to boost organizational performance.

mindfit.title: Mindfit
mindfit.description: Mindfit is a React Native application developed to promote physical, mental health and well-being, aligned with the Society 5.0 vision. Using artificial intelligence, Mindfit offers a personalized experience, focusing on physical activity, nutrition and emotional balance. This project was developed as part of Phase 3 of the Information Systems course at FIAP.
